\forall x \in A \cap C &\Longleftrightarrow x \in A \wedge x \in C & \text{By definition of intersection} \\
&\Longleftrightarrow x \in B \wedge x \in C & \text{Since } A \subseteq B\\
&\Longleftrightarrow x \in (B \cap C)  & \text{As intersection mandates}
